(78, 'widget_text', 'a:3:{i:1;a:0:{}i:2;a:4:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:516:\"<img class=\"size-full wp-image-31 alignnone\" src=\"http://rarathemesdemo.com/job-board-pro/wp-content/uploads/sites/91/2019/01/logo-15.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" />\r\n\r\n\r\nA job, or occupation, is a person\'s role in society. More specifically, a job is an activity, often regular and often performed in exchange for payment. Many people have multiple jobs. A person can begin a job by becoming an employee, volunteering, starting a business, or becoming a parent. The duration of a job may range from temporary.\";s:6:\"filter\";b:1;s:6:\"visual\";b:1;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}', 'auto'),
